title: Mastering Ember.Js(epub){Zzzzz}

Packed with real-world solutions, working examples, and tips, this book is an essential guide to help you master Ember.js to develop web applications.
This book is aimed at web developers with intermediate level experience in Ember.js. Working knowledge of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript is assumed.
